id=nh-logcatd
name=NetHunter Logcat Daemon v2 (persistent + auto-incident)
version=v2.0
versionCode=2
author=ilyamen
description=8-layer logging — persistent logcat 64MB rotating, hourly dmesg, pstore grab on boot, AUTO-FREEZE panic incidents (last 5 kept forever), boot history (50 boots), module logs, storage budget cap 400MB. Run `nh-collect-logs.sh` to tarball into /sdcard/Download or /data/local/tmp.
